quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  48,1,"Min ngudditanii ma uddital …ďanngungal,"
  48,2,"fii no Allah yaafoma ko ngardin…óaa e bakkaat, e ko sakkitii, e fii no O timminira neema makko on e maa…óa, O feewne e laawol po'occiingol."
  48,3,"e no Allah wallirma ballal tii…óngal."
  48,4,"Ko KaŇčko woni jippin…óo dee∆īere nden e …ďer…óe gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen, fii no …ďe …ďeydora gooŇč…óinal e dow gooŇč…óinal ma…ď…ďe ngal. Ko Allah woodani koneeji kammuuji …óiin e leydi ndin; Allah siforii won'de ganndu…óo, √Ďee√Ī…óo,"
  48,5,"e fii no O naadira gooŇč…óin…ďe wor…ďe …ďen e gooŇč…óin…ďe rew…ďe …ďen, Aljannaaji …ói can…ói ilata ley mum, ko …ď…óe duumotoo…ďe e majji, e no O montira-na…ďe ban…ói ma…ď…ďe …óin. ∆äuum wonii ka Allah, malal mawnungal."
  48,6,"E no O leptira naafiqii…ďe wor…ďe …ďeen e naafiqii…ďe rew…ďe …ďeen, e sirkoo…ďe wor…ďe …ďen e sirkoo…ďe rew…ďe …ďen, sikkoo…ďe Allah sikke bon…óe. Yiiloonde bon…ói ngonii e dow ma…ď…ďe. Allah tikkanii…ďe kadi, O hu…óii …ďe, O hebilanii …ďe Jahannama. Nge bonii ruttorde !"
  48,7,"Ko Allah woodani konuuji kammuuli …óiin e leydi ndin. Allah siforii won'de 'ool…óo, √Ďee√Ī…óo."
  48,8,"Min nulirii ma seedotoo…óo, wewlinoowo, e jeertinoowo,"
  48,9,"fii no gooŇč…óiniron Allah e Nulaa…óo makko on, mawninon mo, teddinon mo, subbunhinano…óon mo bimmbi e kiikii…óe."
  48,10,"Pellet, …ďeen won…ďe ahodude e maa…óa, anndu ko Allah …ďe woni e ahodude. Junngo Allah ngon no dow juu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen. Kala non pirtu…óo, haray ko hoore makko o firtani; kala kadi hunnu…óo ko o ahodi kon e Allah, nde o okkata mo njo…ďdi mawnundi."
  48,11,"Aray nde tultu…ďe jiyaa…ďe e yim…ďe ladde …ďen mbi'ane: ""Jawle amen …óeen e …ďeynguureeji amen …óin sokolinii min. Insinano min"". Hi…ďe wowlira …óem…óe ma…ď…ďe, ko alaa e …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe. Maaku: ""Ko hommbo waawani on ka Allah, si O faandanike on lorra maa hara O faandani on nafa? Wurin Allah siforiino won'de kumpitii…óo ko mgollayno…óon kon."
  48,12,"Wurin on cikkuno Nulaa…óo on e gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen ngartataano fes ka …ďeynguureeji ma…ď…ďe. ∆äuum si…óinaa e …ďer…óe mon; cikku…óon sikke bon…óe, laati…óon yim…ďe halkaa…ďe."
  48,13,"Kala dee mo gooŇč…óinaani Allah e Nulaa…óo makko on, haray Mo…óen keblani yeddu…ďe …ďeen (Yiite) dulbaynge."
  48,14,"Ko Allah heeranii laamagol kammuuji …óiin e leydi ndiin. Himo haforana mo o muuyani, o lepta mo o muuyani. Allah siforii won'de kaforoowo, jurmotoo…óo."
  48,15,"Aray nde luttu…ďe …ďen mbi'a, tuma fokkitanoyton henndagol konu-hoyri ndin: ""ngaccee min njokka on"". Hi…ďe faalaa wa…ótitugol daalol Allah ngol. Maaku: ""On njokkataa min fes. Ko wano mon nii Allah daalirnoo oya tuma"". Ma …ďe mbi'u: ""On a√Īanat min tun woni"". Tigi on, …ďe faamataano si wonaa see…óa."
  48,16,"Maakan tultu…ďe …ďen e yim…ďe ladde …ďeen: ""Arma nde noddete…óon e yim…ďe joomiraa…ďe doole tii…óu…ďe. Ho…ďon …ďe maa…óum …ďe silma. Si on …óoftike, Allah okkat on mbarjaari mo∆ī∆īundi; si on nduŇčtii ii no huccitirno…óon oya tuma, O leptira lepte mu'usuu…óe""."
  48,17,"Bakkaatu fawaaki e hoore …ďum…óo on, wonaa e la∆īoowo on wonaa kadi e nawnu…óon bakkaatu fawii. Kala …óoftii…óo Allah e Nulaa…óo makko on, O naadoyay mo Aljannaaji …ói can…ói ilata senngo ley mum. Kala kadi …óuurnii…óo, O leptiray mo lepte mu'usuu…óe."
  48,18,"GooŇč…óii Allah welano gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen, tuma …ďe ahondiraynoo e maa…óa ka ley lekki kin. O anndi ko woni kon ka …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe, O jippini dee∆īere nden e ma…ď…ďe, O warjorii…ďe uddital …ďadiingal,"
  48,19,"e konu-heyri …óuu…óundi ndi …ďe ke…ď…ďitotoo. Allah siforii won'de pool…óo, √Ďee√Ī…óo."
  48,20,"Allah fodii on konu-heyri …óuu…óundi ndi ke…ď…ďito…óon, O yaccinani on ndii …óoo, o suri juu…óe yim…ďe …ďeen e mo'on, fii yo wonu Ma'ande wonan'de gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen, O fewnira on laawol Pocciingol."
  48,21,"E wo…óndi goo ndi on ha…ótanaali taho, Allah kan no hu…ďindii ndi. Allah siforii won'de ka…ótan…óo kala hu'unde."
  48,22,"Hay si yeddu…ďe …ďeen ha…ďiino on, …ďe huccintinayno …ďabbe ma…ď…ďe …óen, refti …ďe ke…ďataano gi…óo wonaa ballao."
  48,23,"∆äuum ko sunna Alla pe∆ī∆īunoo…óo ko adii. A he…ďantaa laawol Alla ngol, mbattiigu."
  48,24,"Ko KaŇčko woni curan…óo on juu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen e mo'on, e cur…óo juu…óe mon …óen e ma…ď…ďe, ka aynde Makka, …ďaawo O foolni on e ma…ď…ďe. Allah siforii won'de deen…óo ko ngolloton kon."
  48,25,"Ko …ďeen ngoni ko jeddi, …ďe paddii on e Juurlirde Hormorde ndeen, […ďe ha…ói] neldaari ndin nde ndi yottotoo nokku mayri. Si wonaano sabu wor…ďe gooŇč…óin…ďe e rew…ďe gooŇč…óinn…ďe …ďe on nganndataano haa ka…ďon …ďe, bakkaatu he…ďa on e fee ma…ď…ďe, ko aldaa e ganndugol... fii yo Allah naatnu e yurmeende makko nden, on mo O muuyani. Si …ďe seetndondir-no [e gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen], ko pellet, Min leptirayno yeddu…ďe …ďen e ma…ď…ďe, lepte mu'usuu…óe."
  48,26,"Tuma nde …ďeya yeddu…ďe mba…ónoo ka …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe jinngo, jinngo majjiyaŇčkoo…ďe...Allah jippini dee∆īere makko nden e dow Nulaa…óo makko on e gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen, O fawi …ďe konngol gooŇč…óal, …ďe woni …ďur…ďe jojjude e hanndude e maggol. Allah siforii ganndugol kala hu'unde."
  48,27,"GooŇč…óii Allah goonginiranii Nulaa…óo makko on, koy…óol ngol e hoore goonga : Ko maa naaton e juulirde Hormorde ndeen si Allah muuyii, hara ko on hoolii…ďe, femmbu…ďe ko*e mon maa …óuytu…ďe (cukuli), on hulataa. Himo anndi ko on nganndaa. O wa…ói ko wonaa ngol (naatugol makko) …óon, uddital …ďadiingal."
  48,28,"Ko KaŇčko woni Nulir…óo Nulaa…óo makko on peewal e diina goonga, fii yo o fawaka ka e hoore kala diina. Allah yonii seedee."
  48,29,"Muhammdu ko Nulaa…óo Allah. Won'…óu…ďe e makko …ďeen ko √Īaa…óu…ďe e yeddu…ďe …ďeen, yurmondir…ďe hakkunde ma…ď…ďe. A yi'at …ďe hi…ďe ru∆ī∆īa, hi…ďe cujja, hi…ďe …óa…ď…ďira Allah …ďural e welayee. Ma'andeeji ma…ď…ďe …óin no ka j'eece ma…ď…ďe batte cujjugol ngol. Ko …óuum woni ko …ďe ciforaa ka Tawreeta. No …ďe ciforaa ka Linjiila kan, ko wano remuru yaltingu pu…ói mayru, ngu …ďanngini …ói, …ói tekki, …ói fotondiri e binndeeje majji, hara …óuum no haawna remoo…ďe, fii no [Allah] tikkinira …ďe yeddu…ďe …ďen. Allah fodii e ma…ď…ďe …ďen gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďe ngolli mo∆ī∆īu…ói …óin, haforanal e njo…ďdi mawnundi."
